{"type": "article", "id": 34948, "title": "替猫狗洗澡太累？试试手掌形的莲蓬头｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-11-27T23:09:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 35246, "name": "Design Letters & Friends"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 107, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161127204227O7ljwWfXFyn2dR9V.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Aquapaw</h3><p>每次为宠物洗澡都演变成“猫狗大战”？美国设计团队为此设计了一款结合了刷头和莲蓬头功能的宠物洗澡工具 Aquapaw。使用前需要将浴室里原有的莲蓬头卸下，根据指示安装好配套的转换接头，为 Aquapaw 供水。为宠物洗澡时，只要把它绑在手上，轻轻挤压掌心的按钮或是握拳就能够控制开关了。由于大小和手掌相当，意味着主人们在为宠物洗澡时可以更好地控制住它们。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/aquapaw/aquapaw-pet-bathing-in-the-palm-of-your-hand\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，早鸟价为 30 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204308xqftCRVwAXnkcvsG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204308JRY1MEp9ZqWCsgSj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677941\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611272043083LFoHusVSnzth6eW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611272043092M5pJbAFahSLwE3o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.836765\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>HOOK2 Colour by Design Letters &amp; Friends</h3><p>丹麦设计品牌 <a href=\"http://designletters.dk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Letters &amp; Friends</a> 最近推出了一套名为 HOOK2 Colour 的墙钩。彩色的圆板和和黑色正方形的底座通过一段圆柱相连，侧面看就好像一截钉子。除了用来悬挂比较大的物品之外，圆板背后还隐藏的一个小钩子可以悬挂小物。将它们排列在墙壁上，简单的几何图形也起到了装饰的作用，让人错以为它们是可以摁下的按钮。这是它的<a href=\"http://designletters.dk/webshop/new/hook2-colour.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 27 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204326PArsuOnVxU12hq3M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.451852\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204326NPhn6W2jSZwIQiBl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611272043269KfDMzybGIErSnCL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204326FSM5BImrKdOswC0D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sanskar Mat by Nivida Malhotra</h3><p>以印度传统的席地坐为灵感，设计师 Nivida Malhotra 对垫子进行了一次改良，带来了这款多功能的折叠垫 Sanskar Mat。当你叠出一个三角形的枕头或是正方形的小桌后，只要用两边的线将它们固定住即可。不需要时，垫子也可以折叠后扎紧储存，进一步减轻了占用面积。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204340wOVa1nCPI3vAfRJY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204340lZ60Q1thjBVRv4Ou.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204340t7lJHV40sFNcCezq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.894286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204340BGC5aiF02xEzU9Pu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Enlighten by Candice Daley et al.</h3><p>为了提醒人们意识到待机中的电器其实也在不断耗电，并且养成随手节能的习惯，来自南非开普半岛科技大学（Cape Peninsula University of Technology）的五位工业设计学生带来了这个名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/45530035/Students-React-to-Energy-Crisis-in-South-Africa\" rel=\"nofollow\">Enlighten</a> 的概念配电盘设计。Enlighten 包含了三个接口，允许用户随时调整所使用的插座。当出现待机耗电的情况，配电盘和插座内置的灯光就会点亮，用户只需要摁下这一插座即可完成断电。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201611272044212zno3rqUbR0pSHLG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204421QWzsL3doguOajtlx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div><h3>Lift-ring Battery by Weimin Xu et al.</h3><p>把电池混在一起之后分不清用过的和新的电池？来自广州美术学院的几位学生带来了这款名为 Lift-ring 的概念电池。电池的顶部附带了类似可乐罐拉环的标签，将它撕开后就能很清楚地将用过的电池区分开来。除此之外，这个标签还能解决一些电池难以从电池槽中取出的困扰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016112720444859dWtaZnkeYRJV2X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204448l5gUxqcQ7pEnXf0H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204448WNQw3vR8Up6jIE4u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.761905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Pill Pocket by Orsan Berkay Tuluce &amp; Ahmet Akbulbul</h3><p>相比文字版的用药指南，土耳其的设计学生 Orsan Berkay Tuluce 和 Ahmet Akbulbul 决定用一种更简便直观的方式让患者知道自己该如何服药。他们共同设计的 Pill Pocket 是一个有着可互动页面的药盒，大小差不多刚好能放进胸前的口袋。一改抽屉式的打开方式，Pill Pocket 的正面可以像书籍封面一样掀开。内部是一面可以根据需要调整的服药指南，诸如日服数量、饭前或是饭后服用以及服用时长等信息都是通过贴纸表示的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204504bBlkm2uIjxP4ydSM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204504mSl47hZkcatsuznO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204503qpEvdmYg2uxy3L7C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706875\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161127204504uadAzl52QET4S06W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}